Recording Method:
identifier (Nomen); 
Nomen - nomen string P80068 (structured) 
Nomen - scheme of nomen P80069 - derived, unstructured
Nomen - category of nomen P80078 = tag name, unstructured
Nomen - note on nomen P80071 unstructured
--LA 11/2/2023
Justification for Mapping: ISRN codes use double hyphens -- ZP 6/15/2022
Transformation Notes:
[Manifestation]-->rdam:P30004-->[Nomen]-->rdand:p80068-->"($a)" .  [Nomen]-->rdand:p80069-->"ISRN".  [Nomen]-->rdand:080078-->"Standard Technical Report Number".  [Nomen]-->rdand:p80071-->"($q)". 
--la 11/2/2023 
 Combine multiple $q values; if no punctuation in the record, enclose all occurences of $q in one set of parentheses and separate individual values with " ; " -- ZP 6/15/2022
Notes (Uncategorized): No id.loc.gov IRI for these identifier schemes; ISRN ISO standard ISO 10444 has been withdrawn but STRN ANSI/NISO Z39.23-1997 (S2015) is still maintained.  -- la 11/2/2023

Justification for Mapping: STRN codes use single hyphens -- ZP 6/15/2022
Transformation Notes: [Manifestation]-->rdam:P30004-->"(STRN)" + {value of $a} + "({value of $q})" + " ; " + "({value of $q})" -- ZP 6/15/2022; Combine multiple $q values; if no punctuation in the record, enclose all occurences of $q in one set of parentheses and separate individual values with " ; " -- ZP 6/15/2022
